title: Nasdaq 100 Movers: SBUX, WDC - Nasdaq.com
text: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Western Digital Corp ( WDC  ) topped the list of the day's best performing components of the Nasdaq 100 index, trading up 5.7%. Year to date, Western Digital Corp registers a 64.4% gain.      And the worst performing Nasdaq 100 component thus far on the day is Starbucks Corp. ( SBUX  ), trading down 3.4%. Starbucks Corp. is showing a gain of 45.2% looking at the year to date performance.  makeArticleAd();    Two other components making moves today are eBay ( EBAY  ), trading down 1.6%, and Micron Technology ( MU  ), trading up 5.3% on the day.
